===============================================
ABOUT THIS MOD:
===============================================
*	Provides polls functionality for both users,
	site-wide and groups
*	Derived from the original Polls plugin




===============================================
SUPPORTED VERSIONS:
===============================================
*	Elgg 1.5
*	Elgg 1.6.1




===============================================
INSTALLATION:
===============================================
*	Extract poll.zip into elgg's module directory.
	it is crucial that the extracted directory name is called 'poll'
*	Enable module in admin tools




